# No app relaunch after build

Never kill or relaunch Jot after a build. Only run `xcodebuild` to compile.

**Why:** The app has a built-in updates panel that detects new builds. The user relaunches from there on their own terms.

**How to apply:** After any `xcodebuild` invocation, stop. No `pkill`, no `open`, no `touch` on the .app bundle. Build and move on.
